cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and image processing, specifically on face de-identification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning models, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses privacy concerns, which could fall under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of facial attribute transfer models also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
